<D>__{we got all day.}
<C>__{sara}
<D>__{my baby's sick! cover him up! he's shaking! have some pity.}
<A>__{a third federal, bardolph, chases after the chickens, gathers them up.}
<C>__{sara}
<D>__{i got nothing. i swear.}
<A>__{nym gets close to her, putting his rifle to her chest.}
